import React from "react";
import { Col, Row } from "react-bootstrap";

function Techstack() {
  return (
    <Row style={{ justifyContent: "center", paddingBottom: "50px" }}>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Java</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Javascript</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Python</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">C</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">HTML</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">CSS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">BOOTSTRAP</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">ReactJS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">VueJS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">AngularJS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">NodeJS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">ExpressJS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Django</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Spring Boot</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Selenium</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Jest</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">MySQL</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">PostgreSQL</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">MongoDB</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Oracle</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Firebase</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">AWS</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">GCP</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Microsoft Azure</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Salesforce</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Microsoft BI</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Tableau</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">Figma</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">AdobeXD</Col>
      <Col xs={4} md={2} className="tech-icons">WCAG</Col>
    </Row>
  );
}

export default Techstack;
